Description: Charge <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">15m</font> and deal <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[DamageTable.GreatAxe_Engage1.DmgCoef * 100]}%</font> <img src="lyshineui/images/icons/tooltip/icon_tooltip_slash_opaque" xPadding="4" scale="1.7" yOffset="4"></img>weapon damage when you reach a target. Press basic attack to stop charging and attack early. \n\nThis ability has <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">grit</font>. <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282">(Grit prevents you from being staggered by incoming attacks.)</font>

Charge now deals <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[DamageTable.GreatAxe_Engage1.DmgCoef * 100]} - {[DamageTable.GreatAxe_Engage3.DmgCoef * 100]}%</font> <img src="lyshineui/images/icons/tooltip/icon_tooltip_slash_opaque" xPadding="4" scale="1.7" yOffset="4"></img>weapon damage based on how far you traveled.

During Charge you may press block to execute a swing attack, dealing <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[DamageTable.GreatAxe_Engage_Swing1.DmgCoef * 100]} - {[DamageTable.GreatAxe_Engage_Swing3.DmgCoef * 100]}%</font> <img src="lyshineui/images/icons/tooltip/icon_tooltip_slash_opaque" xPadding="4" scale="1.7" yOffset="4"></img>weapon damage based on how far you traveled.

Extend your axe <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">5m</font>, <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">pulling</font> foes to you and dealing <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[DamageTable.GreatAxe_JudgementsReach.DmgCoef * 100]}%</font> <img src="lyshineui/images/icons/tooltip/icon_tooltip_slash_opaque" xPadding="4" scale="1.7" yOffset="4"></img>weapon damage and <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">staggering</font> struck foes. <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282">\n\nTaunt Gem Compatible: If you have a Carnelian gem equipped in your great axe, this ability inflicts taunt for {[DamageTable.GreatAxe_JudgementsReach.TauntDuration]}s when it hits. (Taunt causes monsters to focus only on you.)</font>
Reap range is now <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">8m</font>.

<font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">Heal</font> yourself for <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[GreatAxeAbilityTable.Upgrade_Greataxe_Reap_Lifesteal.DmgPctToHealth * 100]}%</font> of damage done by Reap.

After pulling, perform a spin attack dealing <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[DamageTable.GreatAxe_JudgementsReach_FA.DmgCoef * 100]}%</font> <img src="lyshineui/images/icons/tooltip/icon_tooltip_slash_opaque" xPadding="4" scale="1.7" yOffset="4"></img>weapon damage.

A powerful overhead attack dealing <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[DamageTable.GreatAxe_Executioner.DmgCoef * 100]}%</font> <img src="lyshineui/images/icons/tooltip/icon_tooltip_slash_opaque" xPadding="4" scale="1.7" yOffset="4"></img>weapon damage. Base damage increased by <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[GreatAxeAbilityTable.Ability_Greataxe_Executioner.BaseDamage * 100]}%</font> to foes below <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[GreatAxeAbilityTable.Ability_Greataxe_Executioner.TargetHealthPercent]}%</font> health.

Execute gains <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">grit</font> during its attack.<font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282">\n\n(Grit prevents you from being staggered by incoming attacks.)</font>

Execute has a <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[GreatAxeAbilityTable.Upgrade_Greataxe_Executioner_CritVsLowHP.CritChance * 100]}%</font> critical chance against foes below <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[GreatAxeAbilityTable.Upgrade_Greataxe_Executioner_CritVsLowHP.TargetHealthPercent]}%</font> health.

Light attacks with your great axe give you a stack of <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">empower</font>, increasing damage by <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Passive_Greataxe_Reaper_DmgOnLight.DMGStandard * 100]}%</font> for <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Passive_Greataxe_Reaper_DmgOnLight.BaseDuration]}s</font>. <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282">(Max {[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Passive_Greataxe_Reaper_DmgOnLight.StackMax]} stacks.)</font>

Hitting at least <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[GreatAxeAbilityTable.Passive_Greataxe_Reaper_HasteOnLight.NumSuccessfulHits]}</font> targets with a great axe light attack grants <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Passive_Greataxe_Reaper_HasteOnLight.MoveSpeedMod * 100]}% haste</font> for <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Passive_Greataxe_Reaper_HasteOnLight.BaseDuration]}s</font>. <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282">(Haste increases movement speed.)</font>

When you critical hit with a great axe, <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">heal</font> yourself for <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[GreatAxeAbilityTable.Passive_Greataxe_Reaper_OnCritHeal.DmgPctToHealth * 100]}%</font> of the damage done.

Increase armor penetration of great axe attacks by <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[GreatAxeAbilityTable.Passive_Greataxe_Reaper_ArmorPenVsLowHP.ArmorPenetration * 100]}%</font> against foes below <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[GreatAxeAbilityTable.Passive_Greataxe_Reaper_ArmorPenVsLowHP.TargetHealthPercent]}%</font> health.

Whenever your attacks are blocked, gain a stack of <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Passive_Greataxe_Reaper_DmgWhenBlocked.DMGStandard * 100]}%</font> damage for <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Passive_Greataxe_Reaper_DmgWhenBlocked.BaseDuration]}s</font>. <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282">(Max {[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Passive_Greataxe_Reaper_DmgWhenBlocked.StackMax]} stacks.)</font>
Critical damage increased by <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[GreatAxeAbilityTable.Passive_Greataxe_Reaper_Crit.CritDamage * 100]}%</font>.

Great axe attacks against foes below <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[GreatAxeAbilityTable.Passive_Greataxe_Reaper_CritVsLowHP.TargetHealthPercent]}%</font> health have <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[GreatAxeAbilityTable.Passive_Greataxe_Reaper_CritVsLowHP.CritChance * 100]}%</font> increased <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">critical chance</font>.

Great axe attacks against foes below <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[GreatAxeAbilityTable.Passive_Greataxe_Reaper_HealVsLowHP.TargetHealthPercent]}%</font> health <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">heal</font> you for <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[GreatAxeAbilityTable.Passive_Greataxe_Reaper_HealVsLowHP.DmgPctToHealth * 100]}%</font> of damage done.

You move <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Ultimate_Greataxe_Reaper.MoveSpeedMod * 100]}%</font> faster and deal <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Ultimate_Greataxe_Reaper.DMGStandard * 100]}%</font> more damage when looking at a foe within <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[SpellDataTable_GreatAxe.Spell_Ultimate_Greataxe_Reaper.Length * 2]}m</font>.

Spin and attack all nearby foes in a <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">2.5m</font> radius, dealing <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[DamageTable.GreatAxe_Whirlwind.DmgCoef * 100]}%</font> <img src="lyshineui/images/icons/tooltip/icon_tooltip_slash_opaque" xPadding="4" scale="1.7" yOffset="4"></img>weapon damage. If you hit a foe, <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">spin again</font>. You can move while spinning. <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282">(Max 4 spins.) (This attack cannot backstab.)</font>\n\nThis ability has <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">grit</font>. <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282">(Grit prevents you from being staggered by incoming attacks.)</font>
Whirlwind's maximum number of spins is increased to <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">7</font>.
Whirlwind's movement speed is increased by <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">100%</font>.

If you have <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[GreatAxeAbilityTable.Upgrade_Greataxe_Whirlwind_DmgWhenFoesNear.NumAroundMe]}</font> or more foes around you, deal <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[GreatAxeAbilityTable.Upgrade_Greataxe_Whirlwind_DmgWhenFoesNear.BaseDamage * 100]}%</font> more damage.

Perform a fast, spinning attack that <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">pulls</font> targets within a <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">2.5m</font> radius closer to you. Deals <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[DamageTable.GreatAxe_Maelstrom.DmgCoef * 100]}%</font> <img src="lyshineui/images/icons/tooltip/icon_tooltip_slash_opaque" xPadding="4" scale="1.7" yOffset="4"></img>weapon damage.<font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282">\n\nTaunt Gem Compatible: If you have a Carnelian gem equipped in your great axe, hits with this ability inflict taunt for {[DamageTable.GreatAxe_Maelstrom.TauntDuration]}s. (Taunt causes monsters to focus only on you.)</font>
Extends Maelstrom's pull range by <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">50%</font>.
Consumes all <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">projectiles</font> while Maelstrom is active.

Maelstrom does an extra spin attack, pulling in foes and dealing <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[DamageTable.GreatAxe_Maelstrom_NoReprieve.DmgCoef * 100]}%</font> <img src="lyshineui/images/icons/tooltip/icon_tooltip_slash_opaque" xPadding="4" scale="1.7" yOffset="4"></img>weapon damage. Additionally it gains <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">grit</font> during its startup.<font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282">\n\n(Grit prevents you from being staggered by incoming attacks.)</font>

An upward swing dealing <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[DamageTable.GreatAxe_GravityWell.DmgCoef * 100]}%</font> <img src="lyshineui/images/icons/tooltip/icon_tooltip_void_opaque" xPadding="4" scale="1.7" yOffset="4"></img>weapon damage and projecting a powerful tear in reality that creates a vortex up to <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[SpellDataTable_GreatAxe.Spell_GreatAxe_GravityWell_Projectile.CastDistance]}m</font> away. The vortex pulls foes within <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[SpellDataTable_GreatAxe.Spell_GreatAxe_GravityWell_Vortex.Radius]}m</font> to its center and <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">roots</font> them for <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[Type_StatusEffectData.GreatAxe_Vortex_Root.BaseDuration]}s</font>.

Foes within the vortex have their movement speed reduced by <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[Type_StatusEffectData.GreatAxe_Vortex.MoveSpeedMod * -100]}%</font> due to the intense gravity.

The collapsing vortex ends after <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">3s</font> with a damaging burst dealing <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[DamageTable.GreatAxe_GravityWell_Burst.DmgCoef * 100]}%</font> <img src="lyshineui/images/icons/tooltip/icon_tooltip_void_opaque" xPadding="4" scale="1.7" yOffset="4"></img>weapon damage.

Increase burst damage by <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[GreatAxeAbilityTable.Upgrade_Greataxe_GravityWell_DmgPerFoe.BaseDamage * 100]}%</font> for each foe caught in the vortex. <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282">(Max {[GreatAxeAbilityTable.Upgrade_Greataxe_GravityWell_DmgPerFoe.MaxNumAroundMe]} targets.)</font>

Allies gain <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Upgrade_Greataxe_GravityWell_ArmorInWell.PhysicalArmor * 100]}% fortify</font> while standing in your well. <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282">(Fortify increases armor)</font>

If you get hit while holding a great axe and are below <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">50%</font> health, gain <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Passive_Greataxe_Mauler_StamVsLowHp.Stamina]}</font> stamina. <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282">({[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Passive_Greataxe_Mauler_StamVsLowHp_Timer.BaseDuration]}s cooldown.)</font>
Heavy attacks with a great axe <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">pull</font> foes closer to you.

Adds <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">grit</font> to great axe heavy attacks. Also grants <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[GreatAxeAbilityTable.Passive_Greataxe_Mauler_HeavyAddGrit.BaseDamageReduction * 100]}%</font> damage reduction while <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">grit</font> is active. <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282">\n\n(Grit prevents you from being staggered by incoming attacks.)</font>

After you cause a <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">pull</font>, your foe is <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">rooted</font> for <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Passive_GreatAxe_Gravity_Root.BaseDuration]}s</font>.

When you block an attack with a great axe, gain <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Passive_Greataxe_Mauler_DmgOnBlock.DMGStandard * 100]}%</font> damage for <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Passive_Greataxe_Mauler_DmgOnBlock.BaseDuration]}s</font>. <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282">(Max {[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Passive_Greataxe_Mauler_DmgOnBlock.StackMax]} stacks.)</font>

While holding a great axe, gain <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Passive_Greataxe_Mauler_DmgWhenFoesNear.DMGStandard * 100]}%</font> damage when <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">3</font> or more foes are within <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[SpellDataTable_GreatAxe.Spell_Passive_Greataxe_Mauler_DmgWhenFoesNear.Radius]}m</font>.

While holding a great axe, gain <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Passive_Greataxe_Mauler_ArmorWhenFoesNear.PhysicalArmor * 100]}%</font> armor when <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">3</font> or more foes are within <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[SpellDataTable_GreatAxe.Spell_Passive_Greataxe_Mauler_ArmorWhenFoesNear.Radius]}m</font>.

Great axe attacks grant a stacking <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Ultimate_Greataxe_Mauler.DMGStandard * 100]}%</font> damage increase for <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Ultimate_Greataxe_Mauler.BaseDuration]}s</font>. <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282">(Max {[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Ultimate_Greataxe_Mauler.StackMax]} stacks.)</font>
